WEBVTT

00:00:15.098 --> 00:00:15.932
"ALERT"

00:00:15.974 --> 00:00:16.766
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS
What's happening?

00:00:16.766 --> 00:00:16.891
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS

00:00:16.891 --> 00:00:18.685
MAYURI KUROTSUCHI'S PRIVATE LAB
REINFORCED WITH FLOODLIGHTS
Massive Spiritual Pressure
approaching from above!

00:00:18.685 --> 00:00:19.894
Massive Spiritual Pressure
approaching from above!

00:00:24.858 --> 00:00:26.276
W-What was that?!

00:00:26.943 --> 00:00:29.738
Something's coming
through the Soul Shield Membrane!

00:00:30.238 --> 00:00:32.073
It's covering up the Seireitei!

00:00:33.158 --> 00:00:34.242
Damn it!

00:00:36.119 --> 00:00:37.120
Jakuho...

00:00:37.912 --> 00:00:39.205
Raikoben!

00:00:46.796 --> 00:00:47.839
Hurry!

00:00:47.881 --> 00:00:49.507
I am, but...!

00:00:49.591 --> 00:00:51.551
What the hell are these things?!

00:01:03.772 --> 00:01:05.023
What the hell...?

00:01:05.398 --> 00:01:06.816
It's trying to bite me!

00:01:07.359 --> 00:01:08.860
We must protect the lab!

00:01:09.986 --> 00:01:11.863
- Kazeshini!
- Hozukimaru!

00:01:11.946 --> 00:01:12.989
Fujikujaku!

00:01:20.789 --> 00:01:22.749
These things are
anything but beautiful!

00:01:26.795 --> 00:01:27.796
Senbonzakura.

00:01:34.761 --> 00:01:35.804
Impossible!

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:06.835
How pathetic...

00:02:07.711 --> 00:02:08.712
You're...!

00:02:09.212 --> 00:02:12.549
Why waste time swatting them
with a sword

00:02:12.590 --> 00:02:14.050
when you can crush them...

00:02:15.677 --> 00:02:17.512
using your Spiritual Pressure?

00:02:29.733 --> 00:02:34.821
I put my hands together and pray

00:02:34.904 --> 00:02:40.035
Why is fate so cruel?

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:45.582
My will to put on a brave face
is about to break

00:02:45.665 --> 00:02:50.712
Everything I do seems to go wrong,
you know?

00:02:51.046 --> 00:02:53.590
Oh, calm down,
I still have faith in you

00:02:53.673 --> 00:02:56.551
Even if we're apart

00:02:56.593 --> 00:03:03.767
Even if you forget about me someday

00:03:04.601 --> 00:03:06.394
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:03:07.103 --> 00:03:09.439
We don't need words
to understand each other

00:03:09.522 --> 00:03:12.400
We're connected on a higher level

00:03:12.484 --> 00:03:17.322
I'm sorry, fate,
but you're full of it

00:03:17.364 --> 00:03:19.949
So let's laugh it off
by putting on a brave face

00:03:19.991 --> 00:03:27.582
With you, I think we can alter fate

00:03:27.916 --> 00:03:33.254
On lonely nights
when I feel like crying

00:03:33.296 --> 00:03:37.008
I will pray for you

00:03:37.133 --> 00:03:39.969
so that I won't leave you all alone

00:04:01.700 --> 00:04:04.327
It's been a while, Rukia Kuchiki.

00:04:04.619 --> 00:04:06.579
Congratulations on your promotion
to lieutenant.

00:04:07.497 --> 00:04:11.167
I'm glad you were rewarded
for your distinguished service.

00:04:12.085 --> 00:04:14.421
Aizen...!
What are you doing here?

00:04:15.046 --> 00:04:16.589
My sentence was lifted.

00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:18.425
Impossible!
Under whose authority?!

00:04:18.550 --> 00:04:19.634
Me.

00:04:20.427 --> 00:04:21.594
Captain Kyoraku?!

00:04:22.387 --> 00:04:25.056
I'm sure you're wondering why,
so I'll just say it.

00:04:25.557 --> 00:04:28.476
It's because I decided
that we needed his help.

00:04:28.685 --> 00:04:29.394
But...!

00:04:29.394 --> 00:04:31.354
Captain Kyoraku,
you can't be serious!

00:04:31.813 --> 00:04:33.189
You're okay with that?!

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:36.985
I can't go along with
using this guy's help!

00:04:37.402 --> 00:04:38.403
Agreed.

00:04:38.820 --> 00:04:41.781
Considering what he's done,
it's utterly unacceptable.

00:04:42.490 --> 00:04:43.408
What a disgrace!

00:04:45.326 --> 00:04:47.829
Is this about defending
your own honor?

00:04:49.539 --> 00:04:51.708
Well, let me tell you something
about the Court Guards.

00:04:53.668 --> 00:04:56.046
Honor won't help us
protect the world.

00:04:57.088 --> 00:05:00.425
And if you ask me, I do not believe
using evil to defeat evil

00:05:00.508 --> 00:05:02.677
is itself an evil act.

00:05:06.389 --> 00:05:08.433
Seems the matter has been settled...

00:05:09.309 --> 00:05:12.854
Now how about removing
the restraints from my hands

00:05:13.104 --> 00:05:15.523
and letting me out of this chair?

00:05:15.523 --> 00:05:16.900
No can do.

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:20.362
Good grief...

00:05:21.029 --> 00:05:23.740
You expect me to get rid of
them while sitting down?

00:05:24.449 --> 00:05:27.118
I'm pretty sure
you can pull it off.

00:05:27.744 --> 00:05:29.204
You give me too much credit.

00:05:29.704 --> 00:05:32.040
Right now I don't have
that kind of power.

00:05:32.624 --> 00:05:35.418
I wasn't talking about whether
you have the power or not.

00:05:37.587 --> 00:05:40.423
I just figured that
you're not the kind of guy

00:05:40.507 --> 00:05:44.761
to just sit quietly and watch
while these eyeball monsters

00:05:44.844 --> 00:05:48.223
try to gnaw at your body. That's all.

00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:02.404
You truly are a piece of work.

00:06:05.281 --> 00:06:06.574
Thanks.

00:06:09.411 --> 00:06:12.330
Run for it!
Retreat back to the lab!

00:06:16.626 --> 00:06:17.752
Hado Number 90...

00:06:20.380 --> 00:06:21.381
Kurohitsugi.

00:06:35.061 --> 00:06:40.108
Kyoraku. You do realize that
your act of freeing Aizen

00:06:40.608 --> 00:06:42.485
is an insult to all of us.

00:06:45.822 --> 00:06:47.115
Yeah, I know...

00:06:47.782 --> 00:06:49.868
Go ahead and beat me up
all you want.

00:06:51.703 --> 00:06:53.830
After we protect the Seireitei,
that is.

00:06:59.711 --> 00:07:01.212
Unbelievable...

00:07:01.379 --> 00:07:04.090
A Kurohitsugi without incantation
to cause this much destruction...

00:07:05.050 --> 00:07:08.720
He may have become more powerful
than when he fought Kurosaki.

00:07:09.387 --> 00:07:10.638
Are you saying he got stronger

00:07:10.722 --> 00:07:12.766
even while he was
detained in Muken?

00:07:13.141 --> 00:07:14.142
Damn monster!

00:07:14.392 --> 00:07:15.477
What do you know...

00:07:15.894 --> 00:07:19.439
It's still intact despite
being struck by my Kurohitsugi.

00:07:20.065 --> 00:07:21.358
Not surprising given that

00:07:21.358 --> 00:07:23.360
it's built the same way
as the cross in Muken.

00:07:24.152 --> 00:07:25.528
It's quite a chair.

00:07:27.989 --> 00:07:29.407
We must destroy the canopy.

00:07:29.699 --> 00:07:30.700
That won't be necessary.

00:07:31.368 --> 00:07:34.412
The gravity from Kurohitsugi
created a fissure in the canopy.

00:07:34.871 --> 00:07:37.957
All I need is to strike it
with my Spiritual Pressure

00:07:38.416 --> 00:07:39.417
and it will collapse.

00:07:41.461 --> 00:07:44.881
Those things earlier were
a torrent of Yhwach's power.

00:07:45.507 --> 00:07:48.843
They likely poured out while trying
to absorb the Soul King's power.

00:07:49.469 --> 00:07:50.679
What makes you say that?

00:07:52.263 --> 00:07:55.433
Can't you sense the change in
Yhwach's Spiritual Pressure?

00:07:56.976 --> 00:07:58.645
It means even the Quincy King

00:07:58.728 --> 00:08:02.565
will need time to fully contain
the Soul King's power.

00:08:03.191 --> 00:08:04.192
Are you serious?

00:08:04.234 --> 00:08:07.028
Urahara! Isn't there any way
to head to the Royal Palace?

00:08:07.195 --> 00:08:08.613
There is. But we need-

00:08:08.738 --> 00:08:10.365
That, too, will not be necessary.

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:13.660
If you have business
at the Royal Palace,

00:08:13.743 --> 00:08:15.662
I will shoot it down for you.

00:08:19.958 --> 00:08:22.043
Shoot down the Royal Palace?!

00:08:22.419 --> 00:08:25.088
No way!
Is that even possible?!

00:08:40.562 --> 00:08:41.688
It's useless.

00:08:42.814 --> 00:08:45.859
Those restraints doesn't eliminate
your Spiritual Pressure.

00:08:46.067 --> 00:08:48.445
It only keeps it near your body.

00:08:49.029 --> 00:08:52.449
But its power to restrain it
is immensely strong.

00:08:53.408 --> 00:08:56.411
You’re looking at the embodiment
of Soul Society technology.

00:08:56.661 --> 00:08:58.455
Have some respect.

00:08:59.456 --> 00:09:01.374
Isn't that right,
Captain Kurotsuchi?

00:09:02.792 --> 00:09:05.628
Those restraints
were never designed

00:09:05.712 --> 00:09:08.506
to eliminate Spiritual Pressure.

00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:10.592
All of our efforts were spent on

00:09:10.675 --> 00:09:13.720
restraining Spiritual Pressure
along with the body.

00:09:14.429 --> 00:09:17.015
I control the extent.

00:09:17.557 --> 00:09:21.227
Did you really believe your power
exceeded my technology?

00:09:21.561 --> 00:09:24.105
How naïve of you, Sosuke Aizen.

00:09:24.939 --> 00:09:29.944
I don't care if you can shoot
the Royal Palace down or not.

00:09:30.487 --> 00:09:35.533
However, it would be humiliating
for me to see you do such a thing

00:09:35.658 --> 00:09:38.119
while in my restraints.

00:09:39.412 --> 00:09:42.082
In that case,
how about setting it to maximum?

00:09:42.791 --> 00:09:46.628
Let's see which is superior;
your technology or my power-

00:09:50.173 --> 00:09:54.552
Sorry, but I've thoroughly observed
your Spiritual Pressure.

00:09:54.928 --> 00:09:57.639
I don't know if it's because of
that black suit of yours...

00:09:57.639 --> 00:10:00.517
but your Spiritual Pressure
is full of holes.

00:10:01.101 --> 00:10:03.937
As long as I can
measure its distribution...

00:10:04.562 --> 00:10:07.190
I can poke the holes
and strip you naked!

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.484
Especially on someone
that can't move.

00:10:09.609 --> 00:10:11.861
It's easier than ripping the legs
off a chicken!

00:10:15.824 --> 00:10:19.869
No way, you're still conscious?
You really are a monster.

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:22.831
Bastards...!

00:10:23.456 --> 00:10:24.708
No matter.

00:10:24.958 --> 00:10:26.751
I neutralized
your Spiritual Pressure.

00:10:26.876 --> 00:10:28.420
You won't be able to move
for a while.

00:10:29.379 --> 00:10:31.798
We can't have you shoot down
the Royal Palace.

00:10:31.881 --> 00:10:34.050
Just sit tight and watch.

00:10:34.843 --> 00:10:39.514
Oh, great. What a perfect time
for the enemies to show up.

00:10:40.515 --> 00:10:41.850
Urahara.

00:10:42.809 --> 00:10:46.354
You guys get started on building
the gate to the Royal Palace.

00:10:46.980 --> 00:10:48.857
We'll handle things out here.

00:10:49.899 --> 00:10:53.361
Good luck.
We'll do our best as well.

00:10:58.867 --> 00:11:02.579
I'm surprised you're still alive,
zombie girl.

00:11:03.038 --> 00:11:06.082
I guess it takes a zombie
to control another zombie.

00:11:07.542 --> 00:11:09.502
Say, Quincies!

00:11:10.337 --> 00:11:15.050
We agree with you about not wanting
the Royal Palace shot down.

00:11:15.342 --> 00:11:18.428
Perhaps you've come to help us?

00:11:19.054 --> 00:11:20.597
Of course not.

00:11:20.722 --> 00:11:22.807
We can't have the Royal Palace
shot down

00:11:22.891 --> 00:11:24.351
while His Majesty is still there.

00:11:24.559 --> 00:11:26.061
Right, of course.

00:11:26.561 --> 00:11:28.688
Then I guess we have no choice
but to fight.

00:11:29.314 --> 00:11:31.358
Do you think you can take us on?

00:11:32.609 --> 00:11:35.612
I've already observed all of you,
so my-

00:11:40.450 --> 00:11:43.787
B-Bazz-B...what...?

00:11:47.123 --> 00:11:48.541
I'm confused.

00:11:49.626 --> 00:11:50.710
We'll give you a hand.

00:11:55.507 --> 00:11:58.426
The Wandenreich exists in
the shadows of the Seireitei.

00:11:59.594 --> 00:12:02.430
Like you,
we can't have the Royal Palace fall

00:12:02.806 --> 00:12:04.432
and destroy the Seireitei.

00:12:05.225 --> 00:12:10.230
And that's why you're helping us?
You expect us to believe that?

00:12:10.563 --> 00:12:12.524
I didn't ask you to believe us.

00:12:12.649 --> 00:12:14.943
Nor did I say it was
without a price.

00:12:15.485 --> 00:12:17.654
I'm saying we want
something in return.

00:12:18.363 --> 00:12:22.617
A cease-fire.
We won't get in your way.

00:12:22.659 --> 00:12:26.287
Or let the other
Stern Ritters either.

00:12:27.455 --> 00:12:30.792
In return, take us with you
to the Royal Palace.

00:12:33.336 --> 00:12:35.380
We're going to go kill Yhwach...

00:12:36.589 --> 00:12:38.091
for abandoning us!

00:12:40.135 --> 00:12:41.553
I see.

00:12:42.637 --> 00:12:45.640
TORRENT OF THE SOUL KING'S POWER

00:13:05.326 --> 00:13:08.455
The guy is just doing
whatever he wants...

00:13:08.705 --> 00:13:12.500
Head Captain. We're ready to
send word throughout the Seireitei.

00:13:13.126 --> 00:13:14.127
Thanks.

00:13:16.713 --> 00:13:19.883
Attention all members of
the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:13:20.300 --> 00:13:23.178
All able personnel
please report immediately to

00:13:23.303 --> 00:13:25.930
the site of the Department of R&D.

00:13:26.556 --> 00:13:30.769
I repeat... Attention all members of
the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:13:31.561 --> 00:13:33.104
You okay?

00:13:33.188 --> 00:13:34.522
Easy now...

00:13:34.647 --> 00:13:37.442
Yes, sir...

00:13:38.068 --> 00:13:41.404
You're in pretty bad shape yourself,
Tenth Seat Kurumadani.

00:13:43.365 --> 00:13:45.867
This is nothing.
Now, c'mon!

00:13:46.576 --> 00:13:47.369
I repeat...

00:13:47.702 --> 00:13:48.036
"INCOMING MESSAGE"

00:13:48.036 --> 00:13:50.622
"INCOMING MESSAGE"
Attention all members of
the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:13:50.622 --> 00:13:50.663
Attention all members of
the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:13:51.456 --> 00:13:54.292
All able personnel
please report immediately to

00:13:54.417 --> 00:13:57.212
the site of the Department of R&D.

00:13:58.380 --> 00:13:59.547
Shino...

00:13:59.631 --> 00:14:00.632
Yeah?

00:14:01.216 --> 00:14:02.759
You can let go now...

00:14:03.468 --> 00:14:06.554
And just leave you behind?
No way!

00:14:07.889 --> 00:14:08.848
I can walk...

00:14:09.391 --> 00:14:10.392
on my own.

00:14:16.439 --> 00:14:17.440
Ow!

00:14:17.857 --> 00:14:19.442
Keep up, okay?

00:14:32.497 --> 00:14:33.373
Ah...

00:14:37.168 --> 00:14:38.461
I need all of your help...

00:14:39.212 --> 00:14:41.881
I need to borrow
your Spiritual Pressure!

00:14:46.886 --> 00:14:47.929
Captain!

00:14:48.179 --> 00:14:49.431
Where's Yachiru?

00:14:49.931 --> 00:14:52.892
Our men are out
looking for her, but still no word...

00:14:58.398 --> 00:14:59.399
Move.

00:15:01.776 --> 00:15:03.570
The other officers
will find her faster

00:15:03.611 --> 00:15:06.781
than if you went yourself,
Captain Zaraki.

00:15:07.532 --> 00:15:10.118
Most importantly,
your power is absolutely necessary

00:15:10.201 --> 00:15:11.369
to build the gate.

00:15:12.162 --> 00:15:14.497
You should be focusing on
the task at hand.

00:15:14.914 --> 00:15:17.167
Am I wrong, Captain Zaraki?

00:15:23.548 --> 00:15:24.841
You're right.

00:15:25.425 --> 00:15:28.970
Our guys can probably
find her faster.

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:41.858
Everyone...

00:15:42.025 --> 00:15:44.027
Thank you all for gathering.

00:15:45.653 --> 00:15:48.198
The enemy has ascended to
the Royal Palace...

00:15:48.365 --> 00:15:52.369
and it appears that Yhwach
has stolen the Soul King's power.

00:15:53.536 --> 00:15:55.872
That's right.
The Soul Society,

00:15:56.373 --> 00:15:59.542
no, the whole world,
is on the brink of destruction.

00:16:00.877 --> 00:16:01.878
At the moment,

00:16:01.961 --> 00:16:04.714
we do not know the status of
Ichigo's group or Squad Zero.

00:16:05.215 --> 00:16:07.550
That leaves us with one mission...

00:16:09.177 --> 00:16:12.430
to stop Yhwach at all costs.

00:16:13.348 --> 00:16:14.516
Do you understand?

00:16:15.266 --> 00:16:17.227
Past grudges are irrelevant now.

00:16:17.769 --> 00:16:20.146
This is our fight.

00:16:21.856 --> 00:16:24.567
What is it that
you risk your lives for?

00:16:25.527 --> 00:16:28.113
Only if we protect the world
will there be

00:16:28.154 --> 00:16:29.572
a path for the Court Guards.

00:16:30.532 --> 00:16:32.409
So let's protect this world...

00:16:33.576 --> 00:16:35.829
in the name of
the 13 Court Guard Squads!

00:16:49.926 --> 00:16:51.428
We're about to create a gate

00:16:51.511 --> 00:16:54.514
that connects this place
with the Royal Palace.

00:16:55.390 --> 00:16:56.516
In other words...

00:16:57.308 --> 00:16:59.436
we will be storming
the Royal Palace.

00:17:00.812 --> 00:17:03.940
Okay! Are you damn
Soul Reapers ready?!

00:17:05.900 --> 00:17:07.068
Hiyori?!

00:17:07.152 --> 00:17:08.570
What the hell are you doing here?

00:17:09.446 --> 00:17:12.407
We're here cuz you forced us to run
your damn errands, remember?!

00:17:12.490 --> 00:17:14.451
Stop asking dumb questions,
you damn baldy!

00:17:14.576 --> 00:17:17.662
Huh? I ain't bald, so I don't know
what you're talkin' about!

00:17:17.787 --> 00:17:19.372
Yeah, yeah, whatever!

00:17:19.456 --> 00:17:21.499
I'll ignore the loud one
with the bowl cut!

00:17:21.583 --> 00:17:23.626
Hear that, Soi Fon?
She's ignoring you.

00:17:23.793 --> 00:17:26.212
This is not a bowl cut.
I'll kill you.

00:17:27.047 --> 00:17:28.298
Here goes!

00:17:31.593 --> 00:17:32.802
It doesn't feel wet...

00:17:33.345 --> 00:17:35.305
This substance formed from
the distortion between

00:17:35.388 --> 00:17:38.600
the Soul Society, the Precipice World,
and the World of the Living.

00:17:38.683 --> 00:17:40.518
It is the source of energy
we'll need

00:17:40.602 --> 00:17:41.936
to head into the Royal Palace.

00:17:42.145 --> 00:17:43.146
It's done.

00:17:43.938 --> 00:17:44.939
Good.

00:17:45.148 --> 00:17:47.942
Love, Lisa, Hachi, Hiyori...

00:17:48.485 --> 00:17:50.695
You'll find your Shihakusho
in the autopsy room.

00:17:51.488 --> 00:17:53.365
Go get changed so you can join us.

00:17:53.448 --> 00:17:54.616
Huh? Wha-!

00:17:55.450 --> 00:17:56.826
- Got it.
- Hey!

00:17:56.868 --> 00:17:58.536
I haven't agreed to anything yet!

00:17:58.661 --> 00:18:00.163
Let go of me, Love!

00:18:00.413 --> 00:18:02.248
Stop your whining.

00:18:02.374 --> 00:18:05.585
Rose, Shinji, and Kensei are
putting their lives on the line.

00:18:06.086 --> 00:18:08.588
We can't just leave like it's
none of our business.

00:18:16.596 --> 00:18:17.597
Wow...!

00:18:18.139 --> 00:18:19.808
You can move already?

00:18:20.392 --> 00:18:22.352
To say I can "move"
would be a bit misleading.

00:18:25.188 --> 00:18:26.481
Now's your chance to kill me.

00:18:28.191 --> 00:18:29.401
You're kidding, right?

00:18:29.859 --> 00:18:32.696
If it were that easy,
I'd have killed you ages ago.

00:18:34.155 --> 00:18:35.532
Seriously...

00:18:35.740 --> 00:18:37.826
You got struck by that attack

00:18:37.909 --> 00:18:40.328
while having
your Spiritual Pressure suppressed...

00:18:40.578 --> 00:18:43.915
and all it did was immobilize you
for five minutes or so.

00:18:44.374 --> 00:18:47.377
I almost feel sorry for
that fallen Quincy over there.

00:18:47.669 --> 00:18:51.464
That was the first time I've ever
been immobilized for five minutes.

00:18:52.424 --> 00:18:54.426
There's no reason for you
to feel bad for him.

00:18:55.218 --> 00:18:56.386
Good point...

00:18:57.178 --> 00:18:59.097
Well, if you're not in
top shape yet,

00:18:59.180 --> 00:19:01.850
then do me a favor
and stay put for a while...

00:19:02.392 --> 00:19:04.144
until the gate's ready.

00:19:12.068 --> 00:19:13.528
We can only use this method

00:19:13.611 --> 00:19:16.406
while Kurosaki has torn a hole
in the membrane.

00:19:17.115 --> 00:19:20.160
There might not be a way to return.

00:19:20.869 --> 00:19:22.537
Seriously?

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:24.122
You're telling us this now?

00:19:24.247 --> 00:19:27.083
I'm sorry.
Please don't get so worked up.

00:19:27.334 --> 00:19:28.585
That's not it!

00:19:29.085 --> 00:19:31.421
Your disrespect for assuming
we would cower

00:19:31.421 --> 00:19:33.048
if you had told us the truth...

00:19:33.131 --> 00:19:35.508
is what upsets me, Kisuke Urahara!

00:19:36.384 --> 00:19:39.387
You were once a member of
the 13 Court Guards.

00:19:39.471 --> 00:19:41.222
You should know better!

00:19:41.890 --> 00:19:45.518
We all feel the same way about
fighting for the Court Guards.

00:19:47.812 --> 00:19:49.939
Respect?
Fighting for the Court Guards?

00:19:50.398 --> 00:19:53.401
I don't care about any of that
or if we can get back or not.

00:19:53.860 --> 00:19:56.905
All I care about is
to go and crush those bastards.

00:19:59.074 --> 00:20:00.575
So stop wasting our time.

00:20:01.618 --> 00:20:03.119
Let's go already.

00:20:05.538 --> 00:20:07.123
You're right.

00:20:08.708 --> 00:20:11.753
Let's get going...together.

00:20:16.091 --> 00:20:18.551
Soul Reapers and Quincies
joining forces...

00:20:19.594 --> 00:20:22.013
So they can protect
the Soul Society together?

00:20:23.098 --> 00:20:24.099
No...

00:20:24.391 --> 00:20:26.518
It's because they happen to
share a common goal...

00:20:27.227 --> 00:20:30.397
to catch up and destroy
the very enemy you're going after.

00:20:31.773 --> 00:20:32.816
Ironic....

00:20:33.400 --> 00:20:35.110
that the one who stopped me...

00:20:35.652 --> 00:20:39.489
would enter the Royal Palace
before me.

00:20:41.032 --> 00:20:43.535
You really are an insufferable man...

00:20:44.119 --> 00:20:45.537
Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:20:47.038 --> 00:20:48.039
Ishida...!

00:20:52.168 --> 00:20:53.169
Kurosaki...

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:54.504
Inoue...

00:20:56.464 --> 00:20:57.674
Thank goodness...

00:20:58.758 --> 00:20:59.759
Inoue!

00:21:00.927 --> 00:21:02.053
You okay, Inoue?!

00:21:02.512 --> 00:21:03.513
Y-Yeah...

00:21:04.639 --> 00:21:07.142
I'm just a bit hungry, that's all.

00:21:07.475 --> 00:21:08.476
What?

00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:09.811
Ichigo...

00:21:09.936 --> 00:21:14.274
Orihime's been healing everyone
without any breaks.

00:21:14.524 --> 00:21:17.485
She fixed my arm,
and your severe injuries, too.

00:21:17.694 --> 00:21:18.778
I see...

00:21:21.656 --> 00:21:23.241
Did Ishida really...

00:21:24.159 --> 00:21:25.160
Yeah...

00:21:25.452 --> 00:21:28.663
So he really did betray us?

00:21:30.540 --> 00:21:31.541
Kon?

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.668
Kon was the real hero.

00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:35.795
When you came falling,

00:21:36.046 --> 00:21:39.132
Kon inflated his body
to act as a cushion and...

00:21:40.342 --> 00:21:41.343
Kon...

00:21:42.093 --> 00:21:43.553
Rest in peace.

00:21:43.678 --> 00:21:45.305
Don't go killing me off!

00:21:45.347 --> 00:21:47.474
Wait, you're still alive?

00:21:47.599 --> 00:21:49.851
Damn right!
You should be grateful, Ichigo.

00:21:50.018 --> 00:21:53.521
It's a good thing I hid inside
your clothes just in case.

00:21:53.563 --> 00:21:55.523
I see.
So you were hiding, huh?

00:21:56.858 --> 00:21:59.319
Stop!
Or I'll go muscle mode and beat-

00:21:59.361 --> 00:22:00.570
- Thanks.
- What?

00:22:03.531 --> 00:22:04.574
Wrong line!

00:22:04.699 --> 00:22:07.077
You're supposed to beat me up

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:10.663
so I can gain sympathy
to boost my popularity!

00:22:10.747 --> 00:22:12.540
Do it!
Come on, Ichigo!

00:22:12.791 --> 00:22:13.792
Now then...

00:22:14.417 --> 00:22:15.919
Ready to mount a counterattack?

00:22:17.671 --> 00:22:19.005
We need to move quick.

00:22:19.297 --> 00:22:20.674
It's been a while since

00:22:20.757 --> 00:22:22.801
the Soul King's Spiritual Pressure
got consumed.

00:22:23.385 --> 00:22:25.053
No telling when this area,

00:22:25.136 --> 00:22:27.555
or the world itself,
will start falling apart.

00:22:27.972 --> 00:22:29.057
Yeah, but...

00:22:29.391 --> 00:22:31.810
First, we need to figure out
how to get back up there.

00:22:32.060 --> 00:22:34.312
We can't get close
without being seen.

00:22:34.396 --> 00:22:35.689
We'll be sitting ducks.

00:22:36.523 --> 00:22:37.899
We won't need to worry about that.

00:22:39.567 --> 00:22:40.568
Open it!

00:22:43.071 --> 00:22:44.739
The way that space is opening up...

00:22:47.575 --> 00:22:48.576
You're...

00:22:49.577 --> 00:22:52.455
Hey. It's been a while, Kurosaki.

00:22:52.539 --> 00:22:53.581
Grimmjow!

00:22:58.753 --> 00:23:02.340
An ache upon
an unsatisfying grayscale

00:23:02.465 --> 00:23:06.344
My confidence vanishes

00:23:13.018 --> 00:23:14.352
I turned regret into lies

00:23:14.436 --> 00:23:16.438
I ignored our chipped blades

00:23:16.521 --> 00:23:18.106
I worked overtime
just for maintenance

00:23:18.189 --> 00:23:20.066
But I knew all along

00:23:20.191 --> 00:23:23.528
that this faded color
was an irreversible law

00:23:23.570 --> 00:23:25.447
So I might as well pray

00:23:25.530 --> 00:23:27.157
There's no turning back now

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:29.159
I thought I had made up my mind

00:23:29.200 --> 00:23:30.910
but I'm still haunted by
doubt and anxiety

00:23:30.994 --> 00:23:32.579
A bundle of emotions torn to shreds

00:23:32.662 --> 00:23:34.456
with nothing left for me to gain

00:23:34.539 --> 00:23:38.376
What's more important
than one's life

00:23:38.460 --> 00:23:41.463
is to shoulder that burden
to sever this monochrome

00:23:41.546 --> 00:23:46.301
I keep searching for the answer
to an unsolvable thesis

00:23:46.384 --> 00:23:48.428
while making choices until I die

00:23:48.511 --> 00:23:52.557
Then I remember where we came from

00:23:52.599 --> 00:23:55.477
and the lives
that could never interact

00:23:55.560 --> 00:23:59.272
No one is allowed to use the scale
since it falls apart in an instant

00:23:59.314 --> 00:24:02.650
So, what can I measure
ourselves against?

00:24:02.776 --> 00:24:06.988
Instead, I hold onto your words

00:24:07.072 --> 00:24:09.783
that gave my heart meaning

00:24:09.866 --> 00:24:11.117
It's always a paradox

00:24:11.159 --> 00:24:13.203
The moon waxes
with each regret and sadness

00:24:13.328 --> 00:24:16.915
The massive, unconquerable foe is
the darkness that dwells within me

00:24:16.998 --> 00:24:18.667
I forsook my pride and joy

00:24:18.708 --> 00:24:20.377
but I am still confounded
by this flock of imperfection

00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:22.253
Beyond that white and resentful
midnight sun

00:24:22.337 --> 00:24:24.339
awaits an illusion etched in black

00:24:34.974 --> 00:24:36.226
It looks like it's over.

00:24:38.353 --> 00:24:41.523
His Majesty has taken
every last bit of the Soul King.

00:24:42.482 --> 00:24:43.983
The Soul King is gone now.

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:55.412
From here on...it is a new world.

00:25:03.169 --> 00:25:04.421
"My claws..."

00:25:06.339 --> 00:25:07.507
"will grind you up."

